Package: ShinyAcoustics
Type: Package
Title: Execute a Shiny app for Audio Clip Verification
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simon Gillings
Maintainer: Simon Gillings <simon.gillings@bto.org>
Description: This package contains functions for configuring and executing a
    Shiny app for the verification of short audio chunks. It saves verification
    decisions in a local sqlite database, and includes options to collate batch
    parameters such as location and time period information for downstream use.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    DBI
    RSQLite
    bsicons
    bslib
    ggplot2
    shiny
    shinyFiles
    shinyWidgets
    shinyjs
